  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they-- they were able to make deal with one of them to be an instructor.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they reduced his-- his sentence considerably.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They-- they brought in peoples like-- like them to-- to-- to train us, you see?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they have to-- So we were fully trained in about-- when we came back, we had to forget 90%-- 90% of it, just because this all dirty tricks in-- in that kind of operation.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then we had our parachute training there in Manchester, about nine-- nine miles.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I keep forgetting.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I discard things, all in a book, the place where we had our parachute training and-- and our-- what went on.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Some-- some pleasant things, like my incident with Merline who jumped in the-- in one of the night-- night-- night jumps.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She-- she jumped ahead of me, and she landed on me really-- really funny, because it was real-- real dark you see.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there was no question of dark or no dark or fog in-- in England.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "A time came you just had to-- had to jump and make-- make our practice jumps, because you never know, in-- in an operation, what kind of night you gonna-- you gonna hit.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So and many times, they selected precisely, intentionally, the toughest situation, the tough situation and places and so-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] to-- to train for this kind of things.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After Manchester, where did you go?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, and then-- well, after the parachute-- parachute jump, because it was something, you see, that-- that really excited you, and-- and they-- they-- they made-- made you a nervous wreck and so on, because that-- that event was so specialized, not like the paratroops and so on, but it was specialized.",
      "word_count": 52
    }
  ],
